105
00:09:15,379 --> 00:09:20,423
Well, yes and no. Your husband is sedated from the angioplasty

106
00:09:20,511 --> 00:09:25,611
but he suffered major heart failure, he could be unconscious for a while yet.

107
00:09:29,096 --> 00:09:32,173
Would it have mattered if I had found him sooner?

108
00:09:32,359 --> 00:09:34,549
Well in medicine, earlier is always better…

109
00:09:35,069 --> 00:09:37,176
but you called as soon as you could, right?

110
00:09:44,288 --> 00:09:45,118
Dan?

111
00:09:48,472 --> 00:09:51,221
Dan! Dan! Can you hear me?!

112
00:09:51,662 --> 00:09:53,381
Deb? Deb.

113
00:09:53,462 --> 00:09:54,221
What?!

114
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,480
You better hope I die!

115
00:10:00,873 --> 00:10:02,286
