116
00:10:05,071 --> 00:10:07,963
Here. Dial it yourself.

117
00:10:09,311 --> 00:10:10,084
Deb.

118
00:10:10,658 --> 00:10:14,763
You know; I came here to apologise. To tell you I was sorry,

119
00:10:15,343 --> 00:10:20,472
even though you’ve been the assiest ass on the planet for the better part of our married lives.

120
00:10:21,415 --> 00:10:23,724
- What are you doing?
- I’m considering, Dan.

121
00:10:24,527 --> 00:10:28,127
Please. Help me.

122
00:10:37,959 --> 00:10:38,751
Dan?

123
00:10:48,577 --> 00:10:49,570
I’m sorry.

124
00:11:01,578 --> 00:11:02,308
Keith.

125
00:11:03,983 --> 00:11:04,945
Gee, who died?

126
00:11:06,669 --> 00:11:07,690
It’s Dan.

127
00:11:08,631 --> 00:11:09,702
He had a heart attack.

128
00:11:16,588 --> 00:11:18,550
Haley, have you seen my grey t-shirt?

129
00:11:27,008 --> 00:11:28,974
I wanna do something, okay?

130
00:11:35,896 --> 00:11:36,495
Haley.

131
00:11:37,704 --> 00:11:40,776
No, it’s okay. It’s okay.

132
00:11:56,702 --> 00:11:58,010
I could love you forever.

133
00:11:59,065 --> 00:12:00,073
So could I.

134
00:12:02,684 --> 00:12:04,420
You’re my family now, Haley.

135
00:12:05,252 --> 00:12:06,565
The true thing I have.

136
00:12:09,023 --> 00:12:10,351
I never wanna lose you.

137
00:12:11,706 --> 00:12:12,567
You won’t.

138
00:12:17,248 --> 00:12:17,999
What?

139
00:12:22,212 --> 00:12:23,134
Marry me.

140
00:12:25,323 --> 00:12:27,267
- Stop it.
- What, would you?

141
00:12:27,439 --> 00:12:29,918
- Oh, you’re embarrassing me. 
- Why not?

142
00:12:31,818 --> 00:12:36,605
- Because… we’re in high school.
- So what? I’m emancipated.

143
00:12:37,613 --> 00:12:39,821
Is this about sex, because I wanna wait?

144
00:12:39,984 --> 00:12:44,439
- No, I can see you caving on that one already.
- Well maybe so.

145
00:12:46,389 --> 00:12:50,532
Nathan, couples don’t get married in high school. It’s just… it’s not normal.

146
00:12:50,655 --> 00:12:55,052
So? I’m not normal. What I’m feeling is definitely not normal

147
00:12:55,862 --> 00:12:59,563
and to be honest with you Haley, I don’t ever want to be normal.

148
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:01,349
Not with you.

149
00:13:04,023 --> 00:13:04,796
I’m serious.

150
00:13:07,151 --> 00:13:08,011
