177
00:15:41,889 --> 00:15:42,786
Coach Durham?

178
00:15:45,857 --> 00:15:46,662
Karen.

179
00:15:47,951 --> 00:15:51,417
I always pretend to be asleep when the nurse comes in here.

180
00:15:52,319 --> 00:15:56,334
