200
00:17:14,399 --> 00:17:15,576
Make some time.

201
00:17:17,901 --> 00:17:19,411
Take a few chances.

202
00:17:29,944 --> 00:17:31,212
Listen, do you hear that?

203
00:17:31,833 --> 00:17:32,681
Hear what?

204
00:17:33,083 --> 00:17:35,298
Silence. It’s nice.

205
00:17:35,610 --> 00:17:38,785
Yeah. At least it was until you started talking.

206
00:17:41,483 --> 00:17:47,104
So what do you want to do after this? I was thinking; maybe some ice-cream, a little lingerie, facial.

207
00:17:47,195 --> 00:17:48,963
