227
00:19:23,281 --> 00:19:24,413
Look Luke…

228
00:19:25,612 --> 00:19:28,677
I want Dan to get better too you know I mean I’m really pulling for him but…

229
00:19:29,512 --> 00:19:33,213
you know my future’s here now, I can’t just… go back.

230
00:19:33,439 --> 00:19:35,871
No I get it. I don’t wanna go back either but…

231
00:19:37,291 --> 00:19:38,569
it just doesn’t feel right.

232
00:19:39,634 --> 00:19:40,326
Okay.

233
00:19:42,077 --> 00:19:43,797
Alright, I’ll tell you what;

234
00:19:45,845 --> 00:19:47,385
gimme reasons to stay.

235
00:19:48,891 --> 00:19:49,649
Keith.

236
00:19:51,005 --> 00:19:53,314
No, I’m serious. Okay?

237
00:19:53,842 --> 00:19:55,010
We’ll make a list.

238
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:58,332
Give me one reason why you don’t wanna go back.

239
00:20:04,324 --> 00:20:06,468
- Dan.
- Ah Dan, see?

240
00:20:06,991 --> 00:20:08,460
Dan’s an ass. That’s good.

241
00:20:11,635 --> 00:20:15,740
