- I screwed up with Brooke and Peyton.

242
00:20:16,448 --> 00:20:17,948
You know, I didn’t even say goodbye.

243
00:20:18,578 --> 00:20:20,840
Not so much as saying it, I just wrote it in a letter.

244
00:20:22,186 --> 00:20:25,495
- You having fun P. Sawyer?
- Hell yes B. Davis, you?

245
00:20:25,899 --> 00:20:26,584
Yeah.

246
00:20:27,947 --> 00:20:32,395
I’ve been thinking about Lucas. It’s not that he left, it's…

247
00:20:32,531 --> 00:20:37,388
